00Z","msg":"廣東話神奇地方係變化多端<br />\n點講都得 <br />\n中英夾雜唔在講<br />\n口語 語法變化萬千<br />\n主胃賓打亂都可以<br />\n我去廁所<br />\n去廁所呀我<br />\n口語書面語用法有別<br />\n字係方塊字非併音字<br />\n難度幾高<br />\n要扮真係幾難<br />\n同埋口音真係一聽就分到"},{"pid":"c9ca40a2cbf21aad00344e5f518aba36d8ae5a93","tid":541184,"uid":82006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa7d2e0eb93894aa6e1478892baa5bf862601e4e","tid":541184,"uid":39365,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"dc1c96154f1f0d8019a63ed5235555ce1113ac1c","tid":541184,"uid":106634,"like":218,"dislike":1,"score":217,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:44:32.000Z","msg":"根本你身邊好撚多講廣多話好撚正宗你以為係香港人，其實根本全撚部係間諜你都仲唔撚知，你聽到有口音以為係間諜嗰啲原來全撚部都係新腥港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"樓下看更都係間碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"講講下又似，佢成日鬼鬼祟祟擺兩隻手係枱下邊，唔知係咪錄緊音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0995b0551970bb9469b096462a791afa7834e9","tid":541184,"uid":86823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"71997139dcc5adb7ff05ff28e7e30cd56f9e57df","tid":541184,"uid":166944,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"35272426a8e220f18cd6162cb616501611a69375","tid":541184,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ifeng.com/phoenixtv/73020791993663488/20070530/908192.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifeng.com%2Fphoenixtv%2F73020791993663488%2F20070530%2F908192.shtml&d=1VqxJALpQ4PnxmeZzgJjrghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6b011fa9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ifeng.com/phoenixtv/73020791993663488/20070530/908192.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在一本名為《我曾經是恐怖分子&mdash;&mdash;金賢姬懺悔錄》的自傳中，金賢姬講述了自己的特工生涯。<br />\n1980年3月，出身於外交官家庭的金賢姬被朝鮮勞動黨&ldquo;調查部&rdquo;選中，接受特工培訓。1983年&ldquo;學成&rdquo;之後，她共接受了三項特工任務。南韓飛機爆炸事件是她&ldquo;職業生涯&rdquo;中第三項、也是最後一項任務。<br />\n金賢姬的第一項任務是和壹名老特工扮成日籍父女，在歐亞大陸周遊了一圈。沒有正式的特別任務，算是老師傅帶著新徒弟&ldquo;出了爐&rdquo;。她的第二項任務就是和另外一名女特工到澳門，學習&ldquo;資本主義的生活方式&rdquo;。<br />\n在她的自傳裏，金賢姬描述了自己是如何受訓的。在澳門，她和她的朝鮮同志們要學習粵語，這樣，當他們被派到海外執行任務的時候，就可以裝扮成香港或者澳門華人。訓練的內容還包括，如何在超市購物、如何使用信用卡，甚至包括如何在迪斯科舞廳娛樂。這些東西，在他們熱愛的祖國統統不存在。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T09:10:52.000Z","msg":"金賢姬的第一項任務是和<span style=\"color: red;\">壹名老特工</span>扮成日籍父女，在歐亞大陸周遊了一圈。沒有正式的特別任務，算是老師傅帶著新徒弟&ldquo;出了爐&rdquo;。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T12:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94ee1a9a9407990e4e0dffdf5bdf4c6aeb41acc","tid":541184,"uid":144372,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd3315279da527a08df80a9637311c5bfb3b919c","tid":541184,"uid":46587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"幾時先有北韓特工上黎開post分享心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"你覺得佢哋會冇人上嚟睇？"},{"pid":"40f8bf13eba4700c5bd4079a4bd306b0820d118e","tid":541184,"uid":92178,"like":19,"dislike":6,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"167972abacce1672d7903472b755739dbe6fc085","tid":541184,"uid":92178,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pi